// One of \.[GFtoDVI]'s little duties is to be a mini-\TeX: It must be able
// to typeset the equivalent of `\.[\\hbox\[]$\langle$string$\rangle$\.\]' for
// a given string of ASCII characters, using either the title font or the
// label font.
//
